  "title": {
    "en": "LONDY Colorful Dreamer 100-Piece Fort Building Kit",
    "zh": "LONDY Colorful Dreamer 100件彩色堡垒拼搭套装"
  },
  "summary": {
    "en": "A 100-piece ball and rod tent and make a fort toy set with five rod colors, orange and yellow connector balls, clips, flag, blanket, and storage bag.",
    "zh": "100件彩色堡垒套装，含五色杆、橙黄连接球、夹子、旗子、印花毯和收纳袋。"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": [
      "The 100-piece LONDY Colorful Dreamer set uses five-color 40 cm PP rods with yellow and orange 5.6 cm connector balls for a bright ball and rod tent.",
      "The box includes clips, a decorative flag, printed blanket, handbook, and storage bag. EN71 CE certification is listed for this model.",
      "Packed set price is $20.44. Color box reference is 42 x 30 x 8 cm, with about 2.5 kg quoted weight.",
      "The bright color-box pack works well for retail shelves, gift channels, kids tent building kit programs, and OEM/ODM packaging."
    ],
    "zh": [
      "100件 LONDY Colorful Dreamer 采用五色 40cm PP 杆，搭配黄色和橙色 5.6cm 连接球。",
      "套装包含夹子、装饰旗、印花毯、说明书和收纳袋；该型号标注 EN71 CE 认证。",
      "单盒合计价格 $20.44，彩盒参考尺寸为 42 x 30 x 8 cm，报价重量约 2.5 kg。",
      "明亮彩盒适合零售货架、礼品渠道和 OEM/ODM 包装。"
    ]
  },
